captions.text:
I wrote a song
for encarnacion
Shall I sing it for you?

♪ and all the children
are gone ♪

♪ I ate some bugs
I ate some grass ♪

♪ I used my hand
to wipe my tears ♪

♪ to kiss your mouth
I'd break my vow ♪

♪ no, no, no
no, no, no way, jose ♪

♪ then we'd break
our vows together ♪
They are ready for you now.

title: Encarnación - Nacho Libre (10/10) Movie CLIP (2006) HD
